  (text "J5 uses the shared custom Pololu_D36V50F6_BEC symbol so VIN/VOUT/GND/EN/PG are named in the schematic. The footprint is direct solder-wire pads so the 6V servo rail does not depend on a single 0.1 inch header pin."
